[b]Simple Flashlight Battery System[/b]

Adds a configurable battery system to the Garry's Mod flashlight. Good for horror, survival, hide and seek, or any server that wants flashlights to matter a little more.

[b]Features[/b]
[list]
[*]Battery drain, recharge, cooldown, and low-battery warnings
[*]Configurable HUD with optional admin-controlled layout
[*]Battery pickup entities with optional random map spawns
[*]Optional support for suit batteries recharging the flashlight
[*]Compatibility support for Better Flashlight
[/list]

[b]Settings[/b]

Players can adjust their HUD when the server allows it. Admins can tune battery drain, recharge behavior, pickups, notifications, and flashlight addon compatibility from the spawnmenu.

